<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Important 6 Week Challenge Details</title>
</head>

<body
  style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Poppins'; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: white; text-align: center;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; background:white;">
    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/YBNsXrk/Group-84-2x.png" alt="Group 84@2x" border="0"
      style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
  </div>
  <div style="width: 100%;">
    <div
      style="background-color: rgba(150, 150, 150, 0.5); max-width: 660px; text-align: center; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.95;">
      <div
        style="width: 100%; max-width: 660px; color: #000; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(60deg, #ECF4FE, #d7dfe9); background-position: center; background-size: cover; box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(5px); opacity: 0.95;">
        <div
          style="padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; background-color: #4B66EA; text-align: center;">
          <h1
            style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.5; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);">
            Welcome to the <br> 6 Week SAT Challenge</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 2rem; text-align: left;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;">Congratulations,<span
              style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #0a3f4c, #0c6278, #0a5c50, #0a5c50); -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; -webkit-background-clip: text;">{{
              parentName }}!</span>,<span
              style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #0a3f4c, #0c6278, #0a5c50, #0a5c50); -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; -webkit-background-clip: text;">{{
              studentName }}!</span>, is registered for the 6 Week SAT Challenge with College Mastermind!</h3><br>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;"><b>You got a great deal because you paid ABSOLUTELY NOTHING
              ($5,000 VALUE).</b></p><br>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;">
            As a 6 Week SAT Challenge participant, {{ studentName }} will get access to all of the materials and
            resources needed to increase [HIS/HER] SAT score quickly!
          </p><br>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;">
            <b>All of the details will be sent in a few minutes</b> with all of the important details! Make sure you
            read every part carefully so that you don’t miss anything.
          </p><br>
          <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">What’s Included</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 20px; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 15px;">
              <li style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px;">Unlimited access to our proven curriculum</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px;">Unlimited access to video solutions and support videos
              </li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px;">3 live virtual group classes per week</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px;">Unlimited support with your questions through the chat
                feature</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px;">7 full-length proctored exams with immediate results</li>
            </ul>
          </div><br>
          <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;">
            <p>{{ studentName }} will also have a Family Support Manager who will be able to offer guidance,
              accountability, motivation, and support along the way! </p>
          </div>

          <div
            style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <div style="padding-bottom: 10px;">
              <div style="text-align: center;">
                <p style="color: #0085FF;"><strong>IMPORTANT!</strong></p>
              </div><br>
              <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;"><a href="#">Here is your access link to your</a> <b>College
                  Mastermind</b> Dashboard. You’ll be able to track the progress and attendance for {{ studentName }}
                and any other children you have enrolled with College Mastermind’s test prep or college advising
                programs.<br>
                </b></p><br>
              <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;"> <b>Please follow the link to create a password</b></p><br>
              <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; padding: 0 2rem;">
                <a href={{ resetLink }}
                  style="text-decoration: none; color: #fff; background-color: #FF7F50; padding: 1rem; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 100ms ease; margin: auto; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block;">LOGIN
                  NOW</a>
                <p style="text-align: center; background-color: #ece9e9;"><b>This link is valid for 1 hour</b></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div><br>
          <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;">
            <p>
              {{ studentName }} was also sent login access to their <b>College Mastermind</b> Dashboard for the 6 Week
              SAT Challenge. Please check-in to see if they registered so that they can keep track of their assignments,
              attendance, and scores.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding: 2rem; text-align: left; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.3rem;">
            <hr style="margin: 0.5rem 0; border: 1px solid #011222;">
            <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #171717;">Thank you for putting your trust in the <b>College
                Mastermind</b> team! We look forward to partnering with you throughout your test prep and college
              admissions journey!</p><br>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;">Kind regards,</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #171717;"><b>Erin Donovan<br>C.O.O. College Mastermind</b></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>